.landing-connect
  .container
    .row
      .col-sm-offset-2.col-sm-8.col-md-offset-3.col-md-6.text-center
        %img{src: '/img/ollert-logo-white.svg', width: '100%'}
    .row
      .col-xs-12.text-center.h1
        Learn what your Trello boards aren't telling you.
    .row
      .text-center
        %a{class: "btn btn-primary btn-xl connect-btn", href: "javascript:void(0)", onClick: "TrelloController.authorize()"}
          Connect to Get Started
    .row
      .text-center.small
        By connecting, you agree to our <a href="/terms">terms of service</a>.

.landing-info.landing-section
  .container.hidden-xs
    .row.text-center.h1
      .c0l-xs-12
        Why Ollert?
    .row.text-center.h3
      .col-md-3.col-xs-4
        Your Trello boards do a great job telling you the state of today.
      .col-md-offset-1.col-md-4.col-xs-4
        But how do you know what's happened during the past week, month, or year?
      .col-md-offset-1.col-md-3.col-xs-4
        That's where Ollert comes in.
    .row
      .col-md-3.col-xs-4
        %img.img-full{src: '/img/landing-trello.png'}
      .col-md-offset-1.col-md-4.text-center.col-xs-4
        %img.img-less{src: '/img/landing-question.png'}
      .col-md-offset-1.col-md-3.col-xs-4
        %img.img-full{src: '/img/landing-ollert.png'}
  .container.visible-xs-block
    .row.text-center.h1
      Why Ollert?
    .row.text-center.h3
      .col-xs-12
        Your Trello boards do a great job telling you the state of today.
    .row
      .col-xs-12.text-center
        %img{src: '/img/landing-trello.png'}
    .row.text-center.h3
      .col-xs-12
        But how do you know what's happened during the past week, month, or year?
    .row
      .col-xs-12.text-center
        %img{src: '/img/landing-question.png'}
    .row.text-center.h3
      .col-xs-12
        That's where Ollert comes in.
    .row
      .col-xs-12.text-center
        %img{src: '/img/landing-ollert.png'}
.landing-victory.landing-section
  .container
    .row.text-center.h1
      A new way to think about Trello boards.
    .row
      .col-xs-12.text-center.h3
        Instantly see the numbers behind the cards.
    .row
      .col-xs-12
        %img{src: '/img/landing-instantly.png'}
    .row
      .col-xs-12.text-center.h3
        Use Ollert to visualize the progress of your boards.
    .row
      .col-xs-offset-1.col-xs-10
        %img{src: '/img/landing-visualize.png'}

.landing-hook.landing-section
  .container
    .row
      .col-xs-12.h1.text-center.landing-subtitle
        What are you waiting for? It's free.
    .row.text-center.h4
      .col-xs-12
        Connect to Trello, choose a board, and view your stats. It's that easy.
    .row.text-center
      .col-xs-12
        %a{class: "btn btn-primary btn-xl", href: "javascript:void(0)", onClick: "TrelloController.authorize()"}
          Connect to Get Started

.landing-contact.landing-section
  .container
    .row
      .col-xs-12.h1.text-center.landing-subtitle
        Want more information?
    .row.text-center
      .col-xs-12.h4
        %img{src: "/img/icon_email.png", alt: "Email"}
        Contact <a href="mailto:connect@ollertapp.com">connect@ollertapp.com</a>.
    .row.text-center
      .col-xs-12.h4
        %img{src: "/img/icon_twitter.png", alt: "Twitter"}
        Follow us on Twitter <a href="https://twitter.com/OllertApp" target="blank">@OllertApp</a>.
    .row.text-center
      .col-xs-12.h4
        %img{src: "/img/icon_github.png", alt: "Github"}
        Contribute some code on <a href="https://github.com/ollert/ollert" target="blank">Github</a>.
